     values ('Sweet and Sour Sauce I', 'Place the sugar, vinegar, water, soy sauce, ketchup and cornstarch in a medium saucepan, and bring to a boil. Stir continuously until the mixture has thickened.', 'https://images.media-allrecipes.com/userphotos/560x315/12803.jpg', 'NAG_CA', '12', 'asian');
